{"prompt": "Generate a website for a sustainable fashion brand. The website should be elegant and use blue as the brand color.", "code": "<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>Evergreen Threads</title>\n    <style>\n        :root {\n            --brand-blue: #0a4f7a;\n            --secondary-blue: #1e81b0;\n            --text-color: #333333;\n            --background-color: #f4f7f6;\n            --white: #ffffff;\n        }\n\n        body {\n            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n            margin: 0;\n            padding: 0;\n            background-color: var(--background-color);\n            color: var(--text-color);\n            line-height: 1.6;\n        }\n\n        .container {\n            width: 80%;\n            margin: 0 auto;\n            padding: 20px 0;\n        }\n\n        header {\n            background-color: var(--brand-blue);\n            color: var(--white);\n            padding: 20px 0;\n            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n        }\n\n        header h1 {\n            margin: 0;\n            text-align: center;\n            font-size: 2.5em;\n            letter-spacing: 2px;\n        }\n\n        nav {\n            text-align: center;\n            margin-top: 15px;\n        }\n\n        nav a {\n            color: var(--white);\n            text-decoration: none;\n            margin: 0 15px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        nav a:hover {\n            color: var(--secondary-blue);\n        }\n\n        .hero {\n            background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--brand-blue), var(--secondary-blue));\n            color: var(--white);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 80px 0;\n            display: flex;\n            flex-direction: column;\n            align-items: center;\n            justify-content: center;\n        }\n\n        .hero h2 {\n            font-size: 3em;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .hero p {\n            font-size: 1.2em;\n            max-width: 600px;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button {\n            background-color: var(--white);\n            color: var(--brand-blue);\n            padding: 15px 30px;\n            text-decoration: none;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            font-weight: bold;\n            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease;\n        }\n\n        .cta-button:hover {\n            background-color: var(--secondary-blue);\n            color: var(--white);\n        }\n\n        .section {\n            padding: 60px 0;\n            text-align: center;\n        }\n\n        .section h3 {\n            font-size: 2em;\n            margin-bottom: 30px;\n            color: var(--brand-blue);\n        }\n\n        .products, .about, .sustainability {\n            display: flex;\n            justify-content: space-around;\n            flex-wrap: wrap;\n            gap: 30px;\n        }\n\n        .product-item, .about-content, .sustainability-item {\n            flex: 1;\n            min-width: 300px;\n            background-color: var(--white);\n            padding: 30px;\n            border-radius: 8px;\n            box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);\n        }\n\n        .product-item img {\n            max-width: 100%;\n            height: auto;\n            border-radius: 5px;\n            margin-bottom: 20px;\n        }\n\n        .product-item h4 {\n            font-size: 1.5em;\n            margin-bottom: 10px;\n            color: var(--brand-blue);\n        }\n\n        .product-item p {\n            font-size: 0.95em;\n        }\n\n        .about-content p, .sustainability-item p {\n            font-size: 1em;\n            text-align: left;\n        }\n\n        footer {\n            background-color: var(--brand-blue);\n            color: var(--white);\n            text-align: center;\n            padding: 30px 0;\n            margin-top: 40px;\n        }\n\n        footer p {\n            margin: 0;\n        }\n\n        footer a {\n            color: var(--secondary-blue);\n            text-decoration: none;\n        }\n\n        footer a:hover {\n            text-decoration: underline;\n        }\n\n        @media (max-width: 768px) {\n            .container {\n                width: 90%;\n            }\n            .hero h2 {\n                font-size: 2.2em;\n            }\n            .hero p {\n                font-size: 1em;\n            }\n            .products, .about, .sustainability {\n                flex-direction: column;\n                align-items: center;\n            }\n            .product-item, .about-content, .sustainability-item {\n                width: 90%;\n            }\n        }\n    </style>\n</head>\n<body>\n\n    <header>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h1>Evergreen Threads</h1>\n            <nav>\n                <a href=\"#about\">About</a>\n                <a href=\"#products\">Products</a>\n                <a href=\"#sustainability\">Sustainability</a>\n                <a href=\"#contact\">Contact</a>\n            </nav>\n        </div>\n    </header>\n\n    <section class=\"hero\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h2>Timeless Style, Consciously Crafted</h2>\n            <p>Discover fashion that feels good and does good. Explore our collection of sustainable, ethically made apparel.</p>\n            <a href=\"#products\" class=\"cta-button\">Shop Our Collection</a>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"about\" class=\"section\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h3>Our Story</h3>\n            <div class=\"about-content\">\n                <p>At Evergreen Threads, we believe in fashion that respects both people and the planet. Founded on the principles of transparency and ethical production, we craft beautiful, durable clothing designed to last. We meticulously source eco-friendly materials and partner with artisans who share our commitment to fair labor practices.</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"products\" class=\"section\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h3>Featured Products</h3>\n            <div class=\"products\">\n                <div class=\"product-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/0a4f7a/ffffff?text=Organic+Cotton+Tee\" alt=\"Organic Cotton T-Shirt\">\n                    <h4>Organic Cotton Tee</h4>\n                    <p>Soft, breathable, and made from 100% certified organic cotton.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/1e81b0/ffffff?text=Recycled+Wool+Sweater\" alt=\"Recycled Wool Sweater\">\n                    <h4>Recycled Wool Sweater</h4>\n                    <p>Cozy and warm, crafted from premium recycled wool fibers.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"product-item\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/0a4f7a/ffffff?text=Linen+Blend+Pants\" alt=\"Linen Blend Pants\">\n                    <h4>Linen Blend Pants</h4>\n                    <p>Lightweight and elegant, perfect for everyday wear.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <section id=\"sustainability\" class=\"section\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h3>Our Commitment</h3>\n            <div class=\"sustainability\">\n                <div class=\"sustainability-item\">\n                    <h4>Eco-Friendly Materials</h4>\n                    <p>We prioritize natural, organic, and recycled fibers like organic cotton, linen, TENCEL\u2122, and recycled wool to minimize our environmental footprint.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"sustainability-item\">\n                    <h4>Ethical Production</h4>\n                    <p>Our garments are made in factories that ensure fair wages, safe working conditions, and respect for workers' rights.</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"sustainability-item\">\n                    <h4>Reduced Waste</h4>\n                    <p>We employ minimalist design principles and work towards zero-waste production methods, including upcycling and recycling fabric scraps.</p>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n\n    <footer id=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Evergreen Threads. All rights reserved.</p>\n            <p>Contact us at: <a href=\"mailto:info@evergreenthreads.com\">info@evergreenthreads.com</a></p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script>\n        // Simple scroll-to-section functionality\n        document.querySelectorAll('nav a[href^=\"#\"]').forEach(anchor => {\n            anchor.addEventListener('click', function (e) {\n                e.preventDefault();\n                document.querySelector(this.getAttribute('href')).scrollIntoView({\n                    behavior: 'smooth'\n                });\n            });\n        });\n    </script>\n\n</body>\n</html>\n```"}